grat_text: Hey Yen, just wanna pop up and thank you for accompanying me throughout these 4 years, no matter in life or academics. I love how we always play hard and work hard together, having so much fun in between the small breaks in our assignments. It is really good to have someone to spend time with and experience new things and food together. Your rationale and alertness also taught me that I need to think and act carefully while taking into account the consequences of my actions. I recently started to be more anxious as we will soon be moving on to the next phase of life. Your words helped me feel better and less worried about the adaptation process as well as my plans for the future. Although it's almost time for us to say goodbye and part ways, I hope that we can enjoy our upcoming trip to the fullest and stay connected in the future. Don't forget to keep me updated on Instagram after this!
